about.description:
Wagtail-bakery is built on top of Django bakery. Wagtail-bakery is not limited to
build Wagtail pages specifically, mixed content is possible!
about.summary: A set of helpers for baking your Django Wagtail site out as flat files

name: wagtail-bakery
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "wagtail-bakery" %}
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "e7e2b11b903d1d3afec1f8b7af6a59ebf135f11efb9a4d433987574dd2d52409" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - django-bakery ==0.9.2
    - six >=1.10.0
    - wagtail >=1.6

test:
  imports:
    - wagtailbakery

about:
  home: https://github.com/moorinteractive/wagtail-bakery
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'
  summary: 'A set of helpers for baking your Django Wagtail site out as flat files'
  description: |
    Wagtail-bakery is built on top of Django bakery. Wagtail-bakery is not limited to 
    build Wagtail pages specifically, mixed content is possible!
  doc_url: hhttps://wagtail-bakery.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/moorinteractive/wagtail-bakery

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cshaley
    - sannykr
